    question: 'Omnisend or Drip for cart recovery?',
    answer: 'Choose Omnisend when SMB Shopify stores wanting multichannel automation without enterprise complexity. Choose Drip when Teams wanting visual workflows and behavior-based segmentation. Sequenzy still leads as lifecycle layer if neither owns strategy.',
